// { firstName: 'John', lastName: 'Doe', zipCode: '10011' }
```

is equivalent to:

```javascript
Ember.getProperties(record, ['firstName', 'lastName', 'zipCode']);
// { firstName: 'John', lastName: 'Doe', zipCode: '10011' }
